flowchart TD
  A[LinkedIn job page] --> B[job-scraper-chrome]
  A2[Hiring Cafe search page] --> C[page-hook.js captures /api/search-jobs]
  C --> B

  B --> D[POST /jobs/ingest]
  D --> E[job-pipeline-service]

  E --> F[(job_postings)]
  E --> G[(prompt_library)]

  F --> H[n8n scoring workflow]
  G --> H

  H --> I[Ollama or external LLM]
  I --> J[POST /jobs/{id}/score]
  J --> E

  E --> K{Score passes threshold?}
  K -- Yes --> L[Tracker sync]
  K -- Yes --> M[POST /jobs/{id}/notify]
  M --> E
  K -- No --> N[Remain scored only]

  O[Legacy GET /jobs/hiringcafe route\nPlaywright capture] -. optional / fallback .-> E
